    </colorGenerator>
    <tradeTags>
      <li>BasicClothing</li>
    </tradeTags>
	<modExtensions>
			<li Class="RWPaintingTool.PaintableExtension">
				<defaultPalette>
					<colorOne>(79,79,34)</colorOne>
					<colorTwo>(112,135,112)</colorTwo>
					<colorThree>(132,132,192)</colorThree>
				</defaultPalette>
			</li>
	</modExtensions>
	 <researchPrerequisites>
      <li>Heavyarmor</li>
    </researchPrerequisites>
  </ThingDef>
	
	
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="ApparelMakeableBase">
    <defName>Stalker_Apparel_Rhino</defName>
    <label>Army exoskeleton "Rhino"</label>
    <description>The next generation of exoskeletons, consisting of a well-reinforced
heavy armored undersuit and an armored M10 gas mask
of Czech manufacture. According to rumors, the idea and early sketches of this
armored suit belonged to the legendary stalker nicknamed Fang,
which after his death ended up at the disposal of other
groups in the Zone If the standard versions of exoskeletons' allow you to feel
safe, then the "Rhino" can make the operator believe that
it is a full-fledged tank, capable of withstanding huge damage,
while having a huge ammunition supply.Such an armored suit is available. perhaps only to the most valuable members
of groups and organizations - and even then those who want to buy it
will have to pay a decent amount.</description>
